Package: Nebulosa
Type: Package
Title: Single-Cell Data Visualisation Using Kernel Gene-Weighted Density Estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Author: c(person("Jose", "Alquicira-Hernandez", email = "j.alquicira@garvan.org.au", rol = "aut, cre"))
Maintainer: Jose Alquicira-Hernandez <j.alquicira@garvan.org.au>
Description: This package provides a enhanced visualization of single-cell gene expression based on gene-weighted density estimation, particularly for recovering the signal fromm dropped-out genes and inspecting the combined expression from a set of genes.
